<h2 style="font-style:normal; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px">文字的居中</h2>

<p><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">对于标准的markdown文本，是不支持居中对齐的。还好markdown支持html语言，所以我们采用html语法格式即可。</span></span></p>

<div style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-align:start">
<pre>
<span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;,Courier,monospace"><code>&lt;center&gt;这一行需要居中&lt;/center&gt;</code></span></span></span>
</pre>
</div>

<h2 style="font-style:normal; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px">文字的字体及颜色</h2>

<h3 style="color:#444444; font-style:normal; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px">字体更换</h3>

<p><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">同样我们也需要遵照其标准的语法格式</span></span></p>

<div style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-align:start">
<pre>
<span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;,Courier,monospace"><code>&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot;&gt;我是黑体字&lt;/font&gt;</code></span></span></span>
</pre>
</div>

<h3 style="color:#444444; font-style:normal; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px">大小更换</h3>

<p><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">大小为size</span></span></p>

<div style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-align:start">
<pre>
<span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;,Courier,monospace"><code>&lt;font face=&quot;黑体&quot; size=10&gt;我是黑体字&lt;/font&gt;</code></span></span></span>
</pre>
</div>

<h3 style="color:#444444; font-style:normal; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px">颜色替换</h3>

<p><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">对于html语音中，颜色是用color来表示，所以可以表示如下</span></span></p>

<div style="-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-align:start">
<pre>
<span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;,Courier,monospace"><code>&lt;font color=red size=72&gt;颜色&lt;/font&gt;</code></span></span></span></pre>
</div>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
